{"tid":1750603,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"對家開大水喉其實好正常","createTime":"2019-11-24T12:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T12:50:30.000Z","uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a1d3d605ec307b30b16db7523f8ac8119de29363","tid":1750603,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:46:54.000Z","msg":"喇，唔好話種票根本唔正常之類嘅嘢，我都知阿媽係女人。<br />\n但係對家玩種票玩多年，知道呢次區選冇晒自動當選，民主派開始發力，港人開始覺醒，唔開大條水喉派晒禮物，一車車廢老咁嚟投票咩<br />\n講到明係選戰，就正如我哋都會吹雞叫自己屋企人同朋友去投票一樣<br />\n<br />\n但係水喉一定會用盡，只靠良心嘅你，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即刻叫齊屋企人去投走建制派，光復區議會</span></span>"},{"pid":"55e252bd24566d4afaa650a6d4a7ef700967e8b1","tid":1750603,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:48:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投資，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"470ed1bb8b342f68ac35c890a20b3448bcc077a8","tid":1750603,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}